data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. Located in a serene and welcoming community, this residence boasts a range of modern features and recent upgrades that make it an ideal choice for your next home. NEW roof in 2022 and NEW 5 ton Carrier AC with transferable warranty in 2021. Tie downs are up to code and HUD plates are visible. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the spacious family room, with vinyl flooring throughout, complete with a cozy fireplace that's perfect for chilly evenings. This inviting space is perfect for relaxation and quality family time. The home features an open floor plan, providing a seamless flow from room to room, making it perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying everyday life. The heart of this home is the beautifully designed spacious kitchen, with plenty of countertop and cabinet space. It's equipped with stainless steel appliances, offering a modern and efficient cooking experience. The breakfast bar is a fantastic addition, allowing for quick meals and a convenient place to gather with family and friends. Just off the kitchen you will find an additional large family room with access to your indoor laundry room. One of the standout features of this home is the luxurious master bedroom, which includes an attached office space, perfect for those who work from home or need a quiet place to study. The en suite bathroom is a true oasis, featuring double sinks, a deep soaking tub, a stand-up shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. It's the perfect retreat after a long day. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms both with walk in closets, and a second full bathroom provide ample space for family members, guests, or a home office. With a total of three bedrooms, there's room for everyone to have their own space. Outside, you'll find a fenced in yard area, and storage shed, providing the perfect setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. The possibilities are endless. Don't miss your opportunity to make this home yours! Schedule your private showing today!
